{"questionId":"22215977","questionHtml":"<p>Calculate the number of months it takes until Imani has at least <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>$</mo><mn>3550</mn></math>&nbsp;in the bank.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>EITHER</strong></p>\n<p><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">I</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>25</mn></math><br></strong><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>PV</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>3000</mn></math><br></strong><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>FV</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3550</mn></math></strong></p>\n<p><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">P</mi><mo>/</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn></math><br></strong><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi><mo>/</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em>(A1)</em>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p><strong> OR&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">I</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>25</mn></math><br></strong><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>PV</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>3000</mn></math><br></strong><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>FV</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3550</mn></math></strong></p>\n<p><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">P</mi><mo>/</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math><br></strong><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi><mo>/</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </strong><strong><em>(A1)</em></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note: </strong>Award <strong><em>A1</em></strong> for all entries correct and opposite signs for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>PV</mi></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>FV</mi></math> values.</p>\n<p><br><br><strong>OR</strong></p>\n<p><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>3550</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>3000</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>25</mn></mrow><mn>1200</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mn>12</mn><mi>N</mi></mrow></msup></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em>(A1)</em></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note: </strong>Award <em><strong>A1</strong></em> for all entries correct.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>THEN</strong></p>\n<p><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">N</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>162</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>161</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>686</mn><mo>…</mo></mrow></mfenced><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mi>months</mi></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em>A1</em></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><strong><em>[2 marks]</em></strong></p>","meta":{"questionId":"22215977","referenceCode":"24M.1.AHL.TZ2.1b","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Calculate the number of months it takes until Imani has at least $3550 in the bank.","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"b","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","SL 1.4—Financial apps – compound interest, annual depreciation","Topic 1—Number and algebra","SL 1.7—Loan repayments and amortization"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}